        <p class="qa-lead">Premium members can access Telegram support groups for updates, guidance, and support.</p>

        <div class="qa-card">
          <ol class="qa-ul" style="padding-left:20px;margin-top:10px;">
            <li>Link your Telegram account (one time)</li>
            <li>Join your assigned groups</li>
            <li>Use the groups for updates and support</li>
          </ol>
          <div class="qa-tip"><strong>If you cannot join:</strong> confirm your subscription is active, then message support with your Telegram username.</div>
        </div>
